title._content: Ashuelot River in Keene New Hampshire

description._content: TITLE Ashuelot River in Keene New Hampshire CREATOR Wardwell, Anne, Keene NH SUBJECT Rivers - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION "Just as the Ashuelot wound through the intervale before man, so it will wind through the city long after these generations have passed. The river, its banks, its surrounding marshes and woods, represent serenity and peace, and provide the ever-changing living beauty without which man's world would be sterile."
